title: Fabulosa 4 in 1 Concentrated Antibacterial Disinfectant All Purpose Cleaner, 220ml, 12 pack, Bliss Baby Powder
features: Kills 99.9% of bacteria and viruses: sanitise and prevent the spread of bacteria and viruses with Fabulosa cleaning products, while keeping your family and pets protected; Fabulosa is vegan friendly and never tested on animals

All purpose liquid: safe to use on most hard surfaces including floors, worktops, tiles, sinks, baby equipment, children’s toys, furniture, door handles, switches, toilets and potties, saving heaps of time

Versatile: use as a floor cleaner, glass cleaner, bathroom cleaner, blind cleaner, surface cleaner, kitchen cleaner and shower cleaner or wipe surfaces, soak sponges and dishcloths and freshen up bins

Cleans and shines: works as a sticky stuff remover from stubborn surfaces, leaving a lasting sparkle around your home, office and car; can be used neat or diluted in water, 1 bottle can make 10 litres of full-strength disinfectant liquid
Long lasting freshness: an active air freshener that eliminates unpleasant odours and leaves behind a fresh comforting scent with a combination of jasmine, rose and vanilla
description: Product Description Keep stocked up on your cleaning supplies with Fabulosa Bliss Baby Powder scented all-purpose antibacterial liquid pack of 12, a must have cleaning solution that can be used neat or diluted in water to make an antibacterial spray. Perfect for the kitchen, bathroom, dining room, laundry room and bedroom. Leave behind an absolutely fabulous aroma as you sterilise your surroundings with Fabulosa’s signature Bliss Baby Powder scent, without harsh chemical smells. Each one of our bottles are made in the UK with love, are cruelty free and vegan friendly! Directions: General disinfection: dilute 1 part Fabulosa with 40 parts water. 1 capful will make 400ml. Neat/undiluted: use undiluted only in ceramic and metal sinks, drains and toilet bowls. Hard surface pet areas: Keep pets off until dry. Do not allow pets to lick or walk on wet treated area. Sprays: dilute and use as a disinfectant spray to create a hygienic and fresh smelling freshness wherever, whenever. We do not recommend usage in food contact areas as Fabulosa is highly perfumed and may taint. Ensure to replace cap after use. Safety information: Caution: may produce allergic reaction. Causes serious eye irritation. Causes skin irritation. Harmful on contact with skin and if swallowed. Harmful to aquatic life with long lasting effects. Wear protective gloves. IF IN EYES: Rinse with plenty of water. Remove contact lenses if present and easy to do so, continue rinsing. IF ON SKIN: Wash with plenty of water. If skin irritation occurs seek medical advice/ attention. If medical advice is needed have product container or label at hand. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. Ingredients: contains amongst other ingredients: Less than 5 percent Non-ionic Surfactants. Ingredients Contains amongst other ingredients: Less than 5% Non-lonic Surfactants, Methanol, Benzalkonium Chloride, Concentrated Perfume, 2-Methyl Undecanal, Citronellol, Dl-Limonene (Racemic), Butylphenyl Methyl-Propional, Alpha-Isomethyl lonone, 1-(2,6,6-Trimethyl-Cyclohexa-1, 3-Dienyl)-2-Buten-1-One
